Package ch.cern.dbod.db.entity

It contains the classes that represent the relational data stored in the database.

See: Description

  • Class Summary

    CommandParam

Package ch.cern.dbod.db.entity Description

It contains the classes that represent the relational data stored in the database. These classes simply define the model, so they don't have to make use of any other package.
